                    </div>
                    <span>This books is a "manual" on facilitation that prepares you very quickly.  Great examples, good checklists, good index - well worth the price.  My only quibble is a small one: charge a few dollars more and improve the paper and printing quality.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Best "how to" book on facilitation with groups and teams.</div>
                    <div>
